review_blob: Dont believe the hype with this one. Lacks body, very thin. Nice meringue head though. Hops are pronounced but expected mango and pineapple not present.

review_blob: Looks and smells delicious! Hops are spot on. Slightly chewy. Nice lacing and legs. BOSH!!
